snippet.title: Sokpop S09: Flipper Volcano - PC Gameplay (Steam)
snippet.description:
Flipper Volcano is a pinball game with procedurally generated levels. Play as a ghost trying to escape an erupting volcano: use your flippers to reach higher levels and outrun the rising lava! Destroy rocks and other obstacles that get in the way and unlock new characters as you play who will help you reach the exit!

Developed by Sokpop Collective
